  canonicalPath="/privacy.html"
  title="DiscVault — Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for the DiscVault iOS app: a privacy-first, self-hosted physical disc collection manager. Learn what data stays on your device, what goes to your own server, and how metadata lookups work."
